, loading UI

custom hook useDataLoadHook .finally(setLoading(false)) immediately call , .finally() function reference function call

setLoading(false) , loading true , LoadingUi component

.finally() callback function , request setLoading(false) 

js
import axios from 'axios';
import { useEffect, useState } from 'react';

const useDataLoadHook = () => {
  const [apps, setApps] = useState([]);
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true);
  const [error, setError] = useState(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    axios('/appsData.json')
      .then(data => setApps(data.data))
      .catch(err => setError(err))
      .finally(() => setLoading(false)); //  function callback  
  }, []);

  return { apps, loading, error };
};

export default useDataLoadHook;
